text: Neal Mohan (born: 1973 or 1974) is an American business executive who is the current CEO of YouTube. Prior to joining YouTube, Mohan worked at Google for several years and played a key role in the development of the company's advertising products, including AdWords and DoubleClick. == References == Category:Pages created with the Article Wizard from 2023 Category:Living people Category:1970s births Category:Businesspeople from Louisiana Category:YouTube Category:People from Lafayette, Louisiana
